official_title: The Feasibility and Acceptability of a Comprehensive Oncology Rehabilitation and Exercise (CORE) Program Among Breast Cancer Survivors
inclusion_criteria:
* Newly diagnosed stage I-III breast cancer survivors who have plans to undergo breast cancer surgery
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
exclusion_criteria: * Stage I-III breast cancer survivors who had received neoadjuvant chemotherapy
